Datasource.Parameter: ( SELECT OGC_FID, geometry, place AS type, name FROM pt_place) AS data
(SELECT OGC_FID, geometry,'building' AS type, name, computedArea as area FROM pg_building) AS data
(SELECT OGC_FID, geometry, landuse AS type, name, computedArea as area FROM pg_landuse WHERE name<>'') AS data
( SELECT OGC_FID, geometry, leisure AS type, name, computedArea as area FROM pg_leisure WHERE name<>'') AS data
(SELECT OGC_FID, geometry, natural AS type, name, computedArea as area FROM pg_natural WHERE name<>'') AS data
(SELECT OGC_FID, geometry, amenity AS type, name, computedArea as area FROM pg_amenity WHERE name<>'') AS data
( SELECT OGC_FID,geometry, highway AS type, name,oneway,ref, LENGTH(ref) AS reflen FROM ln_highway_motorway WHERE (name IS NOT NULL OR ref IS NOT NULL)) AS data
( SELECT OGC_FID,geometry, highway AS type, name,oneway FROM ln_highway_mainroad WHERE (name IS NOT NULL OR oneway IN ('yes', 'true', '1', '-1'))) AS data
( SELECT OGC_FID,geometry, highway AS type, name,oneway FROM ln_highway_minorroad WHERE (name IS NOT NULL OR oneway IN ('yes', 'true', '1', '-1'))) AS data
( select OGC_FID, waterway as type, geometry, name from ln_waterway where waterway in ('river', 'canal', 'stream') AND name IS NOT NULL) AS data
( select OGC_FID, amenity as type, geometry, name from pt_amenity) AS data
( select OGC_FID, 'bus_stop' as type, geometry from pt_public_transport) AS data
